gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 123, Bulls 101
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Bulls, 123-101 tonight in Denver. Nikola Jokic finished with a team-high 28 points along with 16 rebounds and nine assists for the Nuggets, while Michael Porter Jr. tallied 27 points, six rebounds and five 3PT FG in the game. Nikola Vucevic recorded 19 points, seven rebounds and three assists. The Nuggets improve their record to 6-1 with the win, while the Bulls fall to 2-5 for the season.
